            <h1>Housing and building policy</h1>
            <div class="temaMobIngressImg" style="display: none;"><img src="/Upload/KRD/Temabilder/havran150x113.jpg" alt="" /></div>
            <p class="textIngress">Everyone should have an adequate, secure place to live.</p>
            <img src="/Upload/KRD/Temabilder/havran150x113.jpg" alt="" class="temaIngressImg" />
            <div class="descriptionText"><p>Good housing is a necessity for a comfortable and meaningful life. It is important, therefore, to ensure housing for all, according to their needs. The building process should be user-friendly and efficient.&nbsp;All buildings must be secure, and development should focus on universal design, environmental protection and good quality.<br /></p></div>
